The returned list `answer` must not be null.
The length of the returned list `answer` must be equal to the length of arrays `l` and `r`.
The values in the returned list `answer` must be of type boolean.
The value at index `i` in the returned list `answer` must be `true` if the subarray `nums[l[i]], nums[l[i]+1], ... , nums[r[i]]` can be rearranged to form an arithmetic sequence.
The value at index `i` in the returned list `answer` must be `false` if the subarray `nums[l[i]], nums[l[i]+1], ... , nums[r[i]]` cannot be rearranged to form an arithmetic sequence.
